OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778613067
OL,3,CAirport style scanners for reopened
OL,4,Cpolice station cells
OL,6,FOne of the largest police forces in
OL,7,Fthe UK will introduce airport-style
OL,8,Fscanners at their newest police
OL,9,Fstation following a critical report.
OL,11,FThe technology is part of a multi-
OL,12,Fmillion-pound renovation of Longsight
OL,13,Fstation, in south Manchester, which
OL,14,Freopens this Thursday with 44 more
OL,15,Fcells to manage the force's surging
OL,16,Farrest rates.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
