FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778613067
OL,3,CAirport style scanners for reopened
OL,4,Cpolice station cells
OL,6,FThe facility has been closed since
OL,7,F2019, but its redesign marks a major
OL,8,Fshift in how Greater Manchester Police
OL,9,F(GMP) detainees are handled in the
OL,10,Fregion.
OL,12,FThe decision to implement scanners
OL,13,Ffollows an "explosive" report in 2024
OL,14,Fby Dame Vera Baird KC which was highly
OL,15,Fcritical of how the force handled
OL,16,Fcustody, particularly regarding the
OL,17,Ftreatment of women and girls.
OL,19,FHer report recommended airport
OL,20,Fscanners to stop "degrading" strip
OL,21,Fsearches, if possible.
OL,26,@|D@ROU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
