FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778613067
OL,3,CAirport style scanners for reopened
OL,4,Cpolice station cells
OL,6,FGMP said the Longsight facility now
OL,7,Fhas dedicated spaces for youth
OL,8,Fdetainees, provisions in cells for
OL,9,Fneurodivergent detainees, and CCTV and
OL,10,Fphoneline in every cell.
OL,12,FOn-site technology will speed up
OL,13,Fprocesses by conducting court hearings
OL,14,Fremotely from the Longsight station,
OL,15,Finstead of having to transport
OL,16,Fdetainees to court for an initial
OL,17,Fhearing after being charged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
