FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778613067
OL,3,CAirport style scanners for reopened
OL,4,Cpolice station cells
OL,6,FThe facility, described by the Chief
OL,7,FConstable of GMP Sir Stephen Watson as
OL,8,Fa "major milestone" for the force, is
OL,9,Fthe first in England to adopt this
OL,10,Fapproach on such a scale.
OL,12,FSir Stephen added: "It offers us more
OL,13,Fspace to put suspects and keep the
OL,14,Fpublic safe, more safety for our staff
OL,15,Fand detainees, and a more modern and
OL,16,Fefficient facility to help GMP
OL,17,Fcontinue its improvements in custody
OL,18,Fprovision.
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@SO]tD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778613067
OL,3,CAirport style scanners for reopened
OL,4,Cpolice station cells
OL,6,F"We have invested significantly in
OL,7,Fleadership and infrastructure to
OL,8,Ftransform our custody service from
OL,9,Fbeing one of concern in 2023, to being
OL,10,Fone of policing's leaders in 2026.
OL,12,F"This means those who need to come
OL,13,Finto our custody, or those who work so
OL,14,Fhard in our custody, can do so with
OL,15,Fthe safety and dignity they should
OL,16,Fexpect."
OL,18,FSir Stephen joined GMP in May 2021,
OL,19,Fwhen the force was in special measures.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
