PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778613067
OL,3,CAirport style scanners for reopened
OL,4,Cpolice station cells
OL,6,FGMP has since gone from one of the
OL,7,Fworst-performing forces to one of the
OL,8,Fbest, doubling its number of arrests
OL,9,Fsince 2021, carrying out five times
OL,10,Fthe number of stop-and-searches and
OL,11,Fsolving more than double the number of
OL,12,Fcrimes.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
